haracter exists, print .  Sample Input  3 aaab baa aaa Sample Output  3 0 -1 Explanation  Test Case 1: \"aaab\"  Removing 'b' at index  results in a palindrome, so we print  on a new line.  Test Case 2: \"baa\"  Removing 'b' at index  results in a palindrome, so we print  on a new line.  Test Case 3: \"aaa\"  This string is already a palindrome, so we print ; however, , , and  are also all acceptable answers, as the string will still be a palindrome if any one of the characters at those indices are removed.","topics":[],"score":2375,"base_score":2375,"python_score":2375,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"Avynn/Cat-GAN","owner":"Avynn","html_url":"https://github.com/Avynn/Cat-GAN","stars":1,"forks":0,"issues":0,"language":"Python","description":"a generative adverserial network created to identify and generate cats","topics":[],"score":2375,"base_score":2375,"python_score":2375,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"treddson/python","owner":"treddson","html_url":"https://github.com/treddson/python","stars":0,"forks":0,"issues":0,"language":"Python","description":"A place to put python practice","topics":[],"score":2375,"base_score":2375,"python_score":2375,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"chrisbenti/BenchAppSnoKingMonitor","owner":"chrisbenti","html_url":"https://github.com/chrisbenti/BenchAppSnoKingMonitor","stars":0,"forks":0,"issues":0,"language":"Python","description":null,"topics":[],"score":2375,"base_score":2375,"python_score":2375,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"leozc/zTalkbot","owner":"leozc","html_url":"https://github.com/leozc/zTalkbot","stars":3,"forks":0,"issues":0,"language":"Python","description":"zTalkbot - gtalk robot on google appengine","topics":[],"score":2374,"base_score":2374,"python_score":2374,"has_pypi":false},{"name":"mjsir911/CrowdNet","owner":"mjsir911","html_url":"https://github.com/mjsir911/CrowdNet","stars":2,"forks":0,"issues":0,"language":"Python","description":"A Generic Neural Network library built from scratch to learn the fundamentals of calculus with back-prop